  "contents": "<div class=\"content markitup-box\">\r\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t此人也在此论坛有官方账号。<br/>\n<br/>\n<br/>\r\n“有讓明朝起死回生的方法嗎？”<br/>\r\nhttps://www.youtube.com/watch?v=CdrMcjnbhAk<br/>\n<br/>\r\n我宁可回到濮地的土司时代，土司时代虽然也不富裕，但是没有暴明的“美人盂”，“肛狗”，“凌迟处死3600刀”，“活煮苗人”，“煮熟广西少民头吃人眼”。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n其实贵州现在也不富裕。与其回到暴明，我宁可当野蛮人。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n这人要么是收了共产党的钱，要么就是欠修理了，当他经过三反五反，镇反，大跃进，大饥荒，反右，文化大革命，严打，天安门飙坦克，活摘器官。不知道那之后他还想不想回到暴明或者说“皇明”。果然是看别人挑担子不累。<br/>\n<br/>\r\n添加一个吃人地图：<br/>\n<a href=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWMzOGNhZDRlZWEwYjIzYTVkNGIwLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNzg4JmhlaWdodD0yMjA0\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWMzOGNhZDRlZWEwYjIzYTVkNGIwLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNzg4JmhlaWdodD0yMjA0\">https://pincong.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWMzOGNhZDRlZWEwYjIzYTVkNGIwLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNzg4JmhlaWdodD0yMjA0</a><br/>\n<a class=\"placeholder\" href=\"url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly9waW5jb25nLnJvY2tzL3VybC9pbWcvYUhSMGNITTZMeTkwWld4bFozSmhMbkJvTDJacGJHVXZaV016T0dOaFpEUmxaV0V3WWpJellUVmtOR0l3TG5CdVp6OTNhV1IwYUQweE56ZzRKbWhsYVdkb2REMHlNakEw\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWMzOGNhZDRlZWEwYjIzYTVkNGIwLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNzg4JmhlaWdodD0yMjA0\"><img alt=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWMzOGNhZDRlZWEwYjIzYTVkNGIwLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNzg4JmhlaWdodD0yMjA0\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://pincong.rocks/url/img/aHR0cHM6Ly90ZWxlZ3JhLnBoL2ZpbGUvZWMzOGNhZDRlZWEwYjIzYTVkNGIwLnBuZz93aWR0aD0xNzg4JmhlaWdodD0yMjA0\" style=\"max-width:100%\"/></a> </div>",
